    <author fullname="Wes Hardaker" initials="W." surname="Hardaker">
      <organization>USC/ISI</organization>
    </author>
    <date year="2018" month="June" day="29"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document introduces a new DNSKEY flag called DELEGATION_ONLY that indicates that the particular zone will never sign zone data across a label. That is, every label (dot) underneath is considered a zone cut and must have its own (signed) delegation.</t>
    </abstract>
